<h1>煽</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">shān</span><span class=alesi>(shan1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 煽 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 煽</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/stir" style="color:black;">stir</a> <a href="/dictionary/up" style="color:black;">up</a>, <a href="/dictionary/incite" style="color:black;">incite</a>, agitate, provoke</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 14<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 14 strokes: <a href="/character/管" title="guan3: pipe, tube, duct; woodwind music">管</a>, <a href="/character/算" title="suan4: count, calculate, figure; plan">算</a>, <a href="/character/需" title="xu1: need, require, must">需</a>, <a href="/character/精" title="jing1: essence; semen; spirit">精</a>, <a href="/character/察" title="cha2: examine, investigate; notice">察</a>, <a href="/character/境" title="jing4: boundary, frontier; area, region">境</a>, <a href="/character/愿" title="yuan4: sincere, honest, virtuous">愿</a>, <a href="/character/模" title="mo2: model, standard, pattern; copy">模</a>, <a href="/character/疑" title="yi2: doubt, question, suspect">疑</a>, <a href="/character/演" title="yan3: perform, put on; exercise">演</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/火" title="Kangxi radical 86">火</a>&nbsp;86.10</p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 3086</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 3159</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/煽动" title="shan1 dong4">煽动</a>, <a href="/dictionary/煽情" title="shan1 qing2">煽情</a>, <a href="/dictionary/煽动性" title="shan1 dong4 xing4">煽动性</a>, <a href="/dictionary/煽阴风" title="shan1 yin1 feng1">煽阴风</a>, <a href="/dictionary/煽动颠覆国家罪" title="shan1 dong4 dian1 fu4 guo2 jia1 zui4">煽动颠覆国家罪</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反革命宣传煽动罪" title="fan3 ge2 ming4 xuan1 chuan2 shan1 dong4 zui4">反革命宣传煽动罪</a>, <a href="/dictionary/煽动颠覆国家政权" title="shan1 dong4 dian1 fu4 guo2 jia1 zheng4 quan2">煽动颠覆国家政权</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">煽[<span style="color:#990000;">shān</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to fan into a flame<br>- to incite<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+717D</p></div>

